---
description: "Cursor rules for this project. General rules"
globs: **/*
alwaysApply: true
---

Always create a feature branch from main for every code change you make.

Always write tests before changing or writing code.

Always run all tests after changes.

Always run lint before committing: `./scripts/lint.sh` (full) or `./scripts/lint.sh --staged` (staged files only). Install the git pre-commit hook once with `./scripts/install-git-hooks.sh`.